author: Harry Fletcher
title: Courtney Barnett shares new Jack White-produced track 'Boxing Day Blues (Revisited)' - Music
text: Courtney Barnett has shared a new song 'Boxing Day Blues (Revisited)' online.The track is the latest Jack White-produced song to be released by Barnett this month, following on from 'Shivers'.Australian singer Barnett will be visiting the UK later this year, coinciding with the release of Sometimes I Sit and Think, and Sometimes I Just Sit.She will play shows in Manchester, Liverpool, Glasgow and more. A second London date was added at The Forum due to popular demand.Her debut album launched earlier this year, and peaked at number 16 in the UK albums chart.
